{"tid":1845753,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"醫護同黑警真係一個天一個地","createTime":"2020-01-27T10:28:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-27T16:27:43.000Z","uid":21220,"like":931,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":83,"replies":[{"pid":"281363f92fe82dfbcd6882325742a31876ccf8b3","tid":1845753,"uid":21220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T10:28:26.000Z","msg":"醫護救人 黑警殺人<br />\n<br />\n半年前爆發反送中示威<br />\n<br />\n黑警可以選擇辭職罷工同香港人同行<br />\n<br />\n但佢地選擇為左份人工 打香港人殺香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n半年後今日武漢肺炎爆發<br />\n<br />\n醫護為左關封救香港人 阻止支那人入境<br />\n<br />\n寧願唔要人工 比人話黑心都好 都要罷工<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n醫護起薪3皮野仲高過黑警 都願意放棄人工<br />\n<br />\n點解大家都住喺香港 醫護可以捨己為人 黑警就咁仆街<br />\n<br />\n支持醫護罷工 準備好同醫護一齊罷<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n黑警死全家"},{"pid":"273778861039e3b15e07e9e9e63023edb57702d2","tid":1845753,"uid":38904,"like":257,"dislike":2,"score":255,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T10:30:16.000Z","msg":"因為死黑警係世界上最劣種嘅生物<br />\n軍隊都重會去打仗打敵人<br />\n黑警打自己人為樂"},{"pid":"8e54c449c834af1e8fe41d7c6c4e56789a712c17","tid":1845753,"uid":312526,"like":87,"dislike":2,"score":85,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T10:33:17.000Z","msg":"幾時有特務醫護？唔夠人手wow依家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nD狗成日都話自己有急救牌<br />\n幫手汁屎汁尿汁嘔物都得拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46a638390d50460d49c29904de8939ff4a313b65","tid":1845753,"uid":21220,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T10:35:11.000Z","msg":"唔好等2月3<br />\n<br />\n29號大家一齊罷<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b90fb6614abf84939cd79e2a56810927a955373","tid":1845753,"uid":550,"like":80,"dislike":1,"score":79,"quote":{"pid":"273778861039e3b15e07e9e9e63023edb5770