eplyTime":"2020-01-27T13:11:56.000Z","msg":"有讀書都冇讀嘅分別囉"},{"pid":"4d2097c12205d536b9af4aa582a6d42a39816b4c","tid":1845753,"uid":113000,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T13:14:03.000Z","msg":"黑警本身就係爛仔<br />\n無論毅進定大畢業都係爛仔黎<br />\n<br />\n點同醫護比"},{"pid":"d2366a40305a5a9e02df265306e05d5a03d4f7e9","tid":1845753,"uid":113155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T13:14:31.000Z","msg":"下，咪撚拎黎比囉。<br />\n護士要入大學，至少都要明愛，讀五年。<br />\n醫生唔洗講啦。<br />\n<br />\n毅進仔有名你叫啦。<br />\n<br />\n點比"},{"pid":"49cd302bf978408f246701d7e6ff1ac730fca409","tid":1845753,"uid":79704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T13:14:42.000Z","msg":"831"},{"pid":"9fc040d89c138d6c6ee6f79292e510efc587057c","tid":1845753,"uid":257622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T13:16:01.000Z","msg":"其實可不可收集病者體液做武器？"},{"pid":"d47b3ebc920b8ea67cb4521cf340a843b2aab040","tid":1845753,"uid":298833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T13:16:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98d266ba40ebf042c3ddba6f53054b6baef44f18","tid":1845753,"uid":65074,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T13:22:31.000Z","msg":"請醫護同全香港一齊罷工<br />\n<br />\n同埋<br />\n<br />\n拒絕醫黑警"},{"pid":"06461010a8032ca9ebcfcd6cf95a66e7bcb78257","tid":1845753,"uid":15195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T13:24:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=378292\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D378292&d=FyFnEhDp3tEmtF3AT420Rosqpp%2BZ5aV1zu33iQ7YiKA%3D&h=18d001bf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D378292&h=aadba497\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=378292</a><br />\n唔封關都不突止<br />\n非本港人士 豁免醫療